00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:19.440
I request to fight!

00:05:20.280 --> 00:05:21.640
How dare you

00:05:22.520 --> 00:05:24.230
judge me?

00:05:24.990 --> 00:05:26.280
All the people of Great Sui

00:05:26.550 --> 00:05:27.430
