00:06:14.520 --> 00:06:15.470
I'm willing

00:06:16.080 --> 00:06:16.990
to die

00:06:16.990 --> 00:06:18.400
for Great Sui.

00:06:20.230 --> 00:06:21.400
Soldiers of Great Sui,

00:06:21.910 --> 00:06:22.750
